HEADWORD: Complimentary
<hw>Com`pli*men"ta*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Expressive
of regard or praise; of the nature of, or containing, a compliment;
<as>as, a <ex>complimentary</ex> remark; a <ex>complimentary</ex>
